 darkness and immobility. The goal of this group is to expand the zone of light beyond its current limit, though they have no clear plan. However, expeditions into the \"zone of immobility\", though quite hazardess, do bring benefits to the settlement, including enhanced reputation for their deity (even in Gyptia). The god's personality and patronage develops as these missions continue.\r\nA spring said to descend beyond known lands and into the desolation provides focus for this settlement and its residents.","fertility":320,"lvl":0,"s":"ewcd"},"a001196":{"xpos":1,"ypos":196,"k":"a001196","fertility":10,"lvl":0,"s":"ewabcd"},"a001197":{"xpos":1,"ypos":197,"k":"a001197","fertility":10,"lvl":0,"s":"ewabcd"},"a001198":{"xpos":1,"ypos":198,"k":"a001198","fertility":10,"lvl":0,"s":"sewabd"},"a001199":{"xpos":1,"ypos":199,"k":"a001199","fertility":10,"lvl":2,"s":"NEwAB"},"a002000":{"xpos":2,"ypos":0,"k":"a002000","fertility":10,"lvl":10,"s":""},"a002001":{"xpos":2,"ypos":1,"k":"a002001","fertility":10,"lvl":10,"s":""},"a002002":{"xpos":2,"ypos":2,"k":"a002002","fertility":10,"lvl":10,"s":""},"a002003":{"xpos":2,"ypos":3,"k":"a002003","fertility":10,"lvl":10,"s":""},"a002004":{"xpos":2,"ypos":4,"k":"a002004","fertility":10,"lvl":10,"s":""},"a002005":{"xpos":2,"ypos":5,"k":"a002005","fertility":10,"lvl":10,"s":""},"a002006":{"xpos":2,"ypos":6,"k":"a002006","fertility":20,"lvl":10,"s":""},"a002007":{"xpos":2,"ypos":7,"k":"a002007","fertility":40,"lvl":10,"s":""},"a002008":{"xpos":2,"ypos":8,"k":"a002008","fertility":20,"lvl":10,"s":""},"a002009":{"xpos":2,"ypos":9,"k":"a002009","fertility":20,"lvl":10,"s":""},"a002010":{"xpos":2,"ypos":10,"k":"a002010","fertility":40,"lvl":10,"s":""},"a002011":{"xpos":2,"ypos":11,"k":"a002011","fertility":20,"lvl":10,"s":""},"a002012":{"xpos":2,"ypos":12,"k":"a002012","fertility":10,"lvl":10,"s":""},"a002013":{"xpos":2,"ypos":13,"k":"a002013","fertility":20,"lvl":10,"s":""},"a002014":{"xpos":2,"ypos":14,"k":"a002014","fertility":10,"lvl":10