uge is also close to Gyptia so horde members on missions to or from Gyptia often stop here for a time. No special goals come to mind. There is some sort of landmark nearby that inspired the horde to create a rest stop here. They have not told us the story.","fertility":320,"lvl":0,"s":"sNwBcD"},"a023178":{"xpos":23,"ypos":178,"k":"a023178","fertility":10,"lvl":2,"s":"NWBD"},"a023179":{"xpos":23,"ypos":179,"k":"a023179","fertility":10,"lvl":2,"s":"SWACD"},"a023180":{"xpos":23,"ypos":180,"k":"a023180","fertility":20,"lvl":0,"s":"nAb"},"a023181":{"xpos":23,"ypos":181,"k":"a023181","fertility":80,"lvl":0,"s":"sc"},"a023182":{"xpos":23,"ypos":182,"k":"a023182","fertility":80,"lvl":2,"s":"NWABD"},"a023183":{"xpos":23,"ypos":183,"k":"a023183","fertility":40,"lvl":2,"s":"WA"},"a023184":{"xpos":23,"ypos":184,"k":"a023184","tname":"Pick Hold","ttype":"dwarf","tale":"Pick Hold is a dwarven settlement of the Pick Flick clan. Picks made by this clan can be used off hand same as main hand. The settlement borders on the old Obspurso torrent. Hence there is something of a canyon in the area even though the ground is fairly level. This canyon is used as a shelter from salsand storms by the settlement and also serves as a somewhat sheltered route for travel to and from Gyptia. They export fine weapons (especially picks), metals, and stones of various worth. Because there is a very large gnoll encampment somewhat nearby they have a Gyptian promise of protection should they need it. They also receive material for their crafts, rare goods, magic, and lore that Gyptia can provide. Goals here are to discover new minerals and prevent the gnolls from expanding. If gnolls should gain control over or discover a source of mineral wealth they will seek to provoke intervention by Gyptia in order to take it from them.\r\nDeities: The clan has a special place in their hearts for Tatenen – the Personification of the first mound of earth to emerge from chaos during creation. Their favorite non-local deities are Thialfakell and Agni.","fertility":640,"lvl":2,"s":"A"},"a023185":{"xpos":23,"ypos":185,"k":"a023185","fertility":10,"lvl":2,"s":"D"},"a023186":{"xpos":23,"ypos":186,"k":"a023186","fertility":20,"lvl":2,"s":"SWD"},"a023187":{"xpos":23,"ypos":187,"k":"a023187","fertility":160,"lvl":0,"s":"SneWbD"},"a023188":{"xpos":23,"ypos":188,"k":"a023188","fertility":10,"lvl":-150,"s":"neabcD"},"a023189":{"xpos":23,"ypos":189,"k":"a023189","fertility":10,"lvl":-150,"s":"seWbc"},"a023190":{"xpos":23,"ypos":190,"k":"a023190","fertility":10,"lvl":-1,"s":"sNeWAc"},"a023191":{"xpos":23,"ypos":191,"k":"a023191","fertility":20,"lvl":0,"s":"sNeWAc"},"a023192":{"xpos":23,"ypos":192,"k":"a023192","fertility":10,"lvl":2,"s":"NWA"},"a023193":{"xpos":23,"ypos":193,"k":"a023193","fertility":10,"lvl":2,"s":"A"},"a023194":{"xpos":23,"ypos":194,"k":"a023194","fertility":10,"lvl":2,"s":""},"a023195":{"xpos":23,"ypos":195,"k":"a023195","fertility":20,"lvl":2,"s":"d"},"a023196":{"xpos":23,"ypos":196,"k":"a023196","fertility":160,"lvl":2,"s":"swd"},"a023197":{"xpos":23,"ypos":197,"k":"a023197","fertility":20,"lvl":150,"s":"NEBCd"},"a023198":{"xpos":23,"ypos":198,"k":"a023198","fertility":10,"lvl":150,"s":"EwBCd"},"a023199":{"xpos":23,"ypos":199,"k":"a023199","fertility":10,"lvl":150,"s":"EwaB"},"a024000":{"xpos":24,"ypos":0,"k":"a024000","fertility":160,"lvl":2,"s":""},"a024001":{"xpos":24,"ypos":1,"k":"a024001","fertility":10,"lvl":2,"s":""},"a024002":{"xpos":24,"ypos":2,"k":"a024002","fertility":10,"lvl":2,"s":""},"a024003":{"xpos":24,"ypos":3,"k":"a024003","fertility":40,"lvl":2,"s":""},"a024004":{"xpos":24,"ypos":4,"k":"a024004","fertility":10,"lvl":2,"s":""},"a024005":{"xpos":24,"ypos":5,"k":"a024005","fertility":40,"lvl":2,"s":""},"a024006":{"xpos":24,"ypos":6,"k":"a024006","fertility":10,"lvl":2,"s":"C"},"a024007":{"xpos":24,"ypos":7,"k":"a024007","fertility":10,"lvl":2,"s":"EC"},"a024008":{"xpos":24,"ypos":8,"k":"a024008","fertility":20,"lvl":2,"s":"EBC"},"a024009":{"xpos":24,"yp