ift","tale":"Thunder Tusk is a group of uplifted wild boar. As with all uplifts these creatures cannot be specialized. They start with the strength, dexterity, and resilience of a boar except that they have human intelligence and wisdom and can use human weapons if they wish to. After they reach maturity they join in the usual twelve ways like other civilized beings. However, the main way must be melee intensive. They must also study other ways besides the first. Some of them study more intellectual ways as well as martial ways. Their main course of study cannot take more than half their time. And also, as with other uplifted creatures they advance in study more slowly than humans, dwarves, or elves. No special goals for the settlement are known. A landmark nearby is sacred to the boars. Sacred places are always a source of conflict. Gyptia's nearness also generates interest and conflict.","fertility":320,"lvl":2,"s":"SNEABC"},"a026179":{"xpos":26,"ypos":179,"k":"a026179","fertility":10,"lvl":0,"s":"nwa"},"a026180":{"xpos":26,"ypos":180,"k":"a026180","fertility":10,"lvl":0,"s":"sac"},"a026181":{"xpos":26,"ypos":181,"k":"a026181","fertility":10,"lvl":2,"s":"NWAB"},"a026182":{"xpos":26,"ypos":182,"k":"a026182","fertility":10,"lvl":2,"s":"A"},"a026183":{"xpos":26,"ypos":183,"k":"a026183","fertility":20,"lvl":2,"s":""},"a026184":{"xpos":26,"ypos":184,"k":"a026184","fertility":20,"lvl":2,"s":""},"a026185":{"xpos":26,"ypos":185,"k":"a026185","fertility":10,"lvl":2,"s":""},"a026186":{"xpos":26,"ypos":186,"k":"a026186","fertility":10,"lvl":2,"s":""},"a026187":{"xpos":26,"ypos":187,"k":"a026187","fertility":10,"lvl":2,"s":""},"a026188":{"xpos":26,"ypos":188,"k":"a026188","tname":"Set’s Companion","ttype":"gnoll","tale":"Set's Companion is a gnoll encampment that worships Wepwawet in conjunction with Set. Wepwawet is a jackal god connected with warfare and the afterlife. Wepwawet is very like Set himself but less powerful --sort of a Set-in-waiting. The encampment, though quite large, is set pretty much off by itself and so is mostly reduced to waylaying wanderers. They would welcome something more interesting or destructive to do. We think they are constantly adding to a temple for their god and sincerely believe that it will lead them to dominion over the whole land.","fertility":1280,"lvl":2,"s":"SCD"},"a026189":{"xpos":26,"ypos":189,"k":"a026189","fertility":10,"lvl":0,"s":"nab"},"a026190":{"xpos":26,"ypos":190,"k":"a026190","fertility":10,"lvl":0,"s":"scd"},"a026191":{"xpos":26,"ypos":191,"k":"a026191","fertility":20,"lvl":2,"s":"NAB"},"a026192":{"xpos":26,"ypos":192,"k":"a026192","fertility":40,"lvl":2,"s":"d"},"a026193":{"xpos":26,"ypos":193,"k":"a026193","fertility":20,"lvl":2,"s":"w"},"a026194":{"xpos":26,"ypos":194,"k":"a026194","fertility":40,"lvl":2,"s":"a"},"a026195":{"xpos":26,"ypos":195,"k":"a026195","fertility":10,"lvl":2,"s":""},"a026196":{"xpos":26,"ypos":196,"k":"a026196","fertility":10,"lvl":2,"s":""},"a026197":{"xpos":26,"ypos":197,"k":"a026197","fertility":40,"lvl":2,"s":""},"a026198":{"xpos":26,"ypos":198,"k":"a026198","fertility":20,"lvl":2,"s":""},"a026199":{"xpos":26,"ypos":199,"k":"a026199","fertility":10,"lvl":2,"s":""},"a027000":{"xpos":27,"ypos":0,"k":"a027000","fertility":80,"lvl":2,"s":""},"a027001":{"xpos":27,"ypos":1,"k":"a027001","fertility":10,"lvl":2,"s":"sc"},"a027002":{"xpos":27,"ypos":2,"k":"a027002","fertility":10,"lvl":10,"s":"SNWABCD"},"a027003":{"xpos":27,"ypos":3,"k":"a027003","fertility":10,"lvl":0,"s":"snabc"},"a027004":{"xpos":27,"ypos":4,"k":"a027004","fertility":20,"lvl":2,"s":"NWABD"},"a027005":{"xpos":27,"ypos":5,"k":"a027005","fertility":160,"lvl":2,"s":"WAD"},"a027006":{"xpos":27,"ypos":6,"k":"a027006","fertility":20,"lvl":2,"s":"WA"},"a027007":{"xpos":27,"ypos":7,"k":"a027007","fertility":20,"lvl":2,"s":"A"},"a027008":{"xpos":27,"ypos":8,"k":"a027008","fertility":40,"lvl":2,"s":""},"a027009":{"xpos":27,"ypos":9,"k":"a027009","fertility":10,"lvl":2,"s":""},"a027010":{"xpos":27,"ypos"