armonia and Paregoros. They still worship Harmonia and Paregoros but have fastened onto a particular aspect of harmony and consolation that spawned a new minor deity, Qetesh Qudshu – A goddess of sexuality and sacred ecstasy from foreign lands. She was adopted into Gyptian religion just before The Transit. Her worshipers did not blend well with the traditional scholars who dominated worship in the main city of Gypia. And so they moved to an outlying area. Their goal is to enjoy life. The challenge is that everything in the environment conspires against this goal. They have made a sizable settlement and are managing quite well so far in spite of everything.","fertility":2560,"lvl":-450,"s":"SABD"},"a031174":{"xpos":31,"ypos":174,"k":"a031174","fertility":10,"lvl":-600,"s":"sneabd"},"a031175":{"xpos":31,"ypos":175,"k":"a031175","fertility":20,"lvl":-450,"s":"sNEAd"},"a031176":{"xpos":31,"ypos":176,"k":"a031176","fertility":20,"lvl":-300,"s":"NEAB"},"a031177":{"xpos":31,"ypos":177,"k":"a031177","fertility":10,"lvl":-300,"s":"sBd"},"a031178":{"xpos":31,"ypos":178,"k":"a031178","fertility":40,"lvl":-150,"s":"NEwABCd"},"a031179":{"xpos":31,"ypos":179,"k":"a031179","fertility":10,"lvl":-150,"s":"EwaB"},"a031180":{"xpos":31,"ypos":180,"k":"a031180","fertility":40,"lvl":-150,"s":"saBcd"},"a031181":{"xpos":31,"ypos":181,"k":"a031181","fertility":40,"lvl":0,"s":"sNeABcd"},"a031182":{"xpos":31,"ypos":182,"k":"a031182","fertility":10,"lvl":2,"s":"NEABC"},"a031183":{"xpos":31,"ypos":183,"k":"a031183","fertility":10,"lvl":2,"s":"EBC"},"a031184":{"xpos":31,"ypos":184,"k":"a031184","fertility":10,"lvl":2,"s":"EBC"},"a031185":{"xpos":31,"ypos":185,"k":"a031185","fertility":20,"lvl":2,"s":"EBC"},"a031186":{"xpos":31,"ypos":186,"k":"a031186","fertility":20,"lvl":2,"s":"EBC"},"a031187":{"xpos":31,"ypos":187,"k":"a031187","fertility":10,"lvl":2,"s":"EBC"},"a031188":{"xpos":31,"ypos":188,"k":"a031188","fertility":20,"lvl":2,"s":"SEBCD"},"a031189":{"xpos":31,"ypos":189,"k":"a031189","ferti